<div class="page" id="page-qa">
  <div class="page-inner" style="max-width:800px;">
    <p class="section-label">Questions</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Q &amp; A</h2>
    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      <div class="faq-question">
        <h3>What's the dress code?</h3>
        <div class="faq-toggle">+</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>We'll share dress code details for each event closer to the date. Think elegant but comfortable — it's the Italian countryside.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      <div class="faq-question">
        <h3>Do I need a visa to visit Italy?</h3>
        <div class="faq-toggle">+</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>U.S. and Canadian passport holders do not need a visa for short stays. Ensure your passport is valid 6+ months beyond travel dates. Other passports — check Schengen requirements. We can provide an invitation letter.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      <div class="faq-question">
        <h3>How do I get from the airport to Petritoli?</h3>
        <div class="faq-toggle">+</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Rent a car or arrange a shuttle. Indicate your travel plans on the RSVP and we'll coordinate group shuttles by arrival time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      <div class="faq-question">
        <h3>What are the accommodation costs?</h3>
        <div class="faq-toggle">+</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>We'll coordinate costs separately with each guest and plan to subsidize a portion. More details after you RSVP.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      <div class="faq-question">
        <h3>Can I extend my trip to travel Italy?</h3>
        <div class="faq-toggle">+</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Absolutely! Rome, Florence, the Amalfi Coast, and Cinque Terre are all within reach. Fly into one city and out of another.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      <div class="faq-question">
        <h3>When is the RSVP deadline?</h3>
        <div class="faq-toggle">+</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Please RSVP by the date on your invitation. The sooner the better — it helps us plan logistics for everyone!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
